Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.79,0:01:07.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  看这巨大冰山多么雄伟壮丽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:07.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, observe the majesty of the mighty iceberg
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.79,0:01:09.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这冰冻的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:09.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This frozen giant
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.47,0:01:12.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一般漂浮在极地地区
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.47,0:01:12.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,normally found floating in polar regions
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.59,0:01:15.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有时会漂流到较为温暖的水域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:15.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can sometimes stray into warmer waters
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.94,0:01:18.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,引发剧烈的气候变化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:18.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,causing dramatic changes in climate
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.05,0:01:20.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进而影响热带海洋生物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:20.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for tropical undersea life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:22.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034,854)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.81,0:01:27.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  看来冬日老人昨晚来拜访我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:25.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, it seems Old Man Winter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:27.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,paid us a visit late last night
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.69,0:01:30.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而他带来的既不是枕头也不是床单
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:30.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he brought with him not a pillow or a sheet
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.77,0:01:32.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而是毯子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:32.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but a blanket
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.32,0:01:34.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,雪做的毯子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:34.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a blanket of snow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:36.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(414,496)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.33,0:01:36.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  从水母田
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:36.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, from Jellyfish Fields
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.61,0:01:38.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到居民的住所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:38.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to residential abodes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:38.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(698,800)}停
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.74,0:01:40.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再到繁忙的市中心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:40.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to bustling downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:40.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(698,800)}行
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.80,0:01:42.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到处只有这种白白的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:42.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's nothing but the white stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.25,0:01:46.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这也引起了本地居民的关注
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:46.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And local residents are taking notice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:07.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(680,784)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.64,0:02:09.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:09.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.73,0:02:13.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,雨滴被冻成了冰晶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:13.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drops of rain frozen into ice crystals?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要利用它们的能量统治世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I shall harness their energy and rule the world
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.74,0:02:19.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:19.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要统治你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish to rule you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.12,0:02:25.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,雪地天使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:25.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snow angel
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可谢谢你了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你站在那吹口哨的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,While you were just standing there whistling
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.59,0:02:40.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人拿雪球来扔我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:40.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,someone threw a snowball at me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.01,0:02:42.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:42.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.76,0:02:44.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那雪球是长这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:44.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did the snowball look like this?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.85,0:02:46.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:46.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,事态很严重  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is serious, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.61,0:02:50.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人想抓我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:50.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone's after me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该得逃出裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I better leave town
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.48,0:02:53.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  是我扔的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:53.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I threw it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.98,0:02:55.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是在打雪仗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:55.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're having a snowball fight
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.98,0:02:56.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:56.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.15,0:02:58.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打雪仗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:58.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snowball fight?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.87,0:03:01.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:01.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to play
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.04,0:03:03.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你得先做一个雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:03.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, first, you have to make a snowball
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.45,0:03:04.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:04.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.28,0:03:05.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:05.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A snowball
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.76,0:03:07.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一定会特别棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:07.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is going to be great
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.21,0:03:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.38,0:03:17.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:17.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能帮我做个雪球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you help me make a snowball?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.23,0:03:20.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行啊  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:20.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.66,0:03:25.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.66,0:03:25.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could you?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.26,0:03:28.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是在打雪仗  忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:28.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a snowball fight, remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.81,0:03:29.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:29.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,温暖火堆  舒服拖鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Warm fire, cozy slippers
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.15,0:03:45.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有热茶  再配上一片柠檬片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:45.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a piping hot cup of tea with a lemon wedge
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这又是何苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do I even bother?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.42,0:03:59.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个能不能小点声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:59.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you two please keep it down?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.34,0:04:03.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚好能来加入我的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:03.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're just in time to enlist in my army
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.13,0:04:06.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加进来就能一起打败粉红威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:06.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Join me and together we'll defeat the Pink Menace
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.69,0:04:09.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以先把你征为见习列兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:09.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can start you off as a buck private
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过只要你努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but with hard work
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,估计你就能升等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,perhaps you can rise through the ranks
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成普通列兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and become a regular private
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.87,0:04:14.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:14.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.48,0:04:17.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过不用了  傻蛋少校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:17.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but no, thanks, Major Stupidity
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.02,0:04:19.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你跟那边的胡扯将军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:19.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You and General Nonsense over there
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.03,0:04:20.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自个儿打去  别拉上我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:20.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will have to fight without me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.11,0:04:22.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,俩都骂到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:22.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got 'em both
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you fool
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没开始就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This was over before it started
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.48,0:04:32.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我认为你必须无条件投
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:32.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will now consider your unconditional surren
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,der
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来这就是他想要的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, that's how he wants it to go down
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.94,0:04:54.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没打中我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:54.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You missed me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.09,0:05:29.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主队得一分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:29.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Score one for the boys back home
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.18,0:05:33.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:33.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.39,0:05:35.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:35.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是让我喜不起来的惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What an unpleasant surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.48,0:05:41.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  猜谜游戏可真是好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:41.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, nothing like a game of charades
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来想跟你说我被雪呛到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was trying to tell you that I was choking on snow
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是雪就化成水了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but the snow melted and turned into water
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后我把水都喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I drank all the water
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.08,0:05:51.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:51.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,now I'm better
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fascinating
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.70,0:05:55.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚干啥来着了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:55.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, where was I?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.00,0:05:57.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:57.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.89,0:05:59.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能借你家厕所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:05:59.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I use your bathroom?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.26,0:06:01.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  上你自己家厕所去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:01.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, go use your own bathroom
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.31,0:06:02.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我憋不到那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:02.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can make it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.63,0:06:03.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能借吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:03.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.23,0:06:03.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:03.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.85,0:06:04.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能借吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:04.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.51,0:06:05.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:05.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.01,0:06:05.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能借吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:05.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.55,0:06:06.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:06.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.22,0:06:06.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能借吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:06.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.80,0:06:07.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那行  赶紧上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:07.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, make it quick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.97,0:06:09.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:09.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救助敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aiding the enemy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我抓了你个正着  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I caught you red-handed, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝我跟你说  我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, SpongeBob, I was just
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥加我这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's on my side
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我根本没有加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I most certainly am not
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就表示他支持我这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then that means he's on my side
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.94,0:06:29.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了海绵宝宝  我也不是你那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:29.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, SpongeBob, I'm not on your side either
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪边的都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on nobody's side
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.25,0:06:34.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幼稚的小屁孩才打雪仗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:34.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snowball fights are for immature children
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.49,0:06:36.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝不会堕落到你们这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:36.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I will not stoop to your level
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.87,0:06:41.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们俩想用雪球互相把脑子砸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you two want to knock
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:41.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,knock each other's brains out with snowballs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就请别把我扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,kindly leave me out of it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.88,0:06:46.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  来把脑子砸出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:46.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob, let's go knock each other's brains out
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  脑子出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick, it's out
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.10,0:06:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下有好戏看了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, there's something I'd actually like to see
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.52,0:07:01.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直接坐前排应该没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:01.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong with getting a front-row seat, I suppose
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.86,0:07:04.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:04.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.44,0:07:05.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:05.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.84,0:07:06.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:06.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.57,0:07:07.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:07.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们应该是要互相把脑子打出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be knocking each other's brains out
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们签了和平条约  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We signed a peace treaty, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.55,0:07:15.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:15.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were right
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小孩子才打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fighting is for children
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我那时误导了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, I misled you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.33,0:07:19.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大人也打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:19.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's for adults, too
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.16,0:07:21.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,和平条约给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:21.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that peace treaty
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.40,0:07:22.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:22.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续战争去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let the war continue
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.18,0:07:25.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  那不是和平条约
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:25.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, that wasn't the peace treaty
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是和平条约的复印件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was a copy of the peace treaty
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  你们两个太容易就放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, you two are giving up too easily
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.59,0:07:33.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  假装我是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:33.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, Patrick, pretend I'm SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And who am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.34,0:07:37.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以当蟹老板吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:37.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I be Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.68,0:07:38.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:38.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.40,0:07:39.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:39.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, why?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是个好领导
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's a good leader
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能不能闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you butt out?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.94,0:07:44.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能对蟹老板这么说话  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:44.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't talk to Mr. Krabs like that, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.48,0:07:45.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:45.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.73,0:07:47.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:47.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你为什么不扔海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, why didn't you hit SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说你是海绵宝宝啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You said you were SpongeBob, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.74,0:07:59.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:07:59.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's true, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, get back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.96,0:08:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我算是知道接下来会怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, I can see where this is going
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.58,0:08:07.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:07.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's just say for all intents and purposes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.80,0:08:10.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我章鱼哥加入这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:10.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I, Squidward, am now part of this war
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.09,0:08:11.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:11.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都加入战争了  那你碉堡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you're in this war, where's your fort?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没碉堡  懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have one, okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.64,0:08:15.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:15.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得有座碉堡才行  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You gotta have a fort, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有碉堡才能取胜  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forts win wars, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.52,0:08:20.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要碉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:20.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want a fort?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.84,0:08:21.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要的碉堡有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:21.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, there's your fort
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.93,0:08:22.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:22.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.41,0:08:24.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那碉堡太小了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:24.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That fort's too small, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.56,0:08:27.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就只是个示范
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:27.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just a demonstration
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.31,0:08:27.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:27.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.61,0:08:28.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说得对  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:28.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's right, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.52,0:08:29.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那玩意保护不了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:29.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That thing would never protect you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小得可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's downright puny
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.08,0:08:32.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相信我  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:32.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trust me, it's fine
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.74,0:08:35.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:35.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它就是太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is too small
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.49,0:08:37.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我蹲下就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:37.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not if I crouch down
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们连个我蹲下的机会都不给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, you didn't even give me a chance to crouch down
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.91,0:08:40.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:40.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在这可以完美做到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Down here, I am perfectly
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,暴露目标
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exposed
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.05,0:08:45.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个能不能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:45.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you two please
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要再扔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stop throwing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.46,0:08:49.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,雪球了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:49.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,snowballs?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.22,0:08:58.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥还击了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:58.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward returned fire
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开战了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then it's war
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对不对  等下等下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, wait, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是在做示范
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just giving a demonstration
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  都够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.61,0:09:15.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是你们自找的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:15.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys asked for it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.24,0:09:19.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:19.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got him
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.24,0:09:20.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:20.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got him
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,中你一脸  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In your face, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还确实有点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was actually kind of
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.08,0:09:29.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:29.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,exciting
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.21,0:09:34.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来就没这么有活力过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:34.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, I've never felt so alive
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他打中你了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He got you good, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.51,0:09:39.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隐蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:39.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take cover
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.35,0:09:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.82,0:09:41.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:41.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.39,0:09:44.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:44.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.23,0:09:45.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:45.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.31,0:09:46.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这回打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:46.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got you that time
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.31,0:09:50.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:50.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.15,0:09:54.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:54.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Incoming
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.61,0:09:56.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:56.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.11,0:09:59.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:09:59.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.41,0:10:02.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥现在好像打得很认真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:02.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think Squidward's taking this really seriously
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.28,0:10:04.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上一把雪球里面还有他竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:04.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That last one had his clarinet in it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来要实施B计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's time for Plan B
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有雪球扔过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The snowballs have stopped falling
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.35,0:10:25.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好利用这段短暂的停火时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:25.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I better take advantage of this momentary cease-fire
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.06,0:10:26.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:26.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.74,0:10:28.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,左侧暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:28.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My left flank is exposed
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.52,0:10:31.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个胖海星会刚刚好打中我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:31.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That bloated starfish is going to run right through me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我马上就补好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just fix that right now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.36,0:10:39.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  这样北墙就成弱点了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:39.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, that makes my north wall a weak spot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可要是他们从后面袭击  我就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But if they attack from the rear, I'm a goner
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.62,0:10:48.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:48.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.46,0:10:52.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是空袭要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:52.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what about the possibility of an aerial attack?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.30,0:10:58.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样应该就能成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:58.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess that ought to do it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.80,0:11:04.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥的碉堡现在几乎刀枪不入了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:04.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fort Squidward is now all but impenetrable
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.14,0:11:11.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些傻子现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:11.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, where are those fools?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一枪已经鸣响了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The first shot has been fired
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接招  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take this, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尝尝我冰冻的怒火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Taste my frozen fury
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胜利属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Victory is mine
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我打中你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got you now
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见什么了吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you hear something, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.80,0:11:33.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:33.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.34,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(313,275)\fsp50\fs150\c&H00FFAF&}蟹老板的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.92\pos(330,472)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:44.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:42.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.92\pos(300,394)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.92\pos(458,318)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.92\pos(316,322)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.92\pos(464,664)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,686)}上品古董出售
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.81,0:11:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  跳蚤市场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, a yard sale
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.20,0:11:51.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,俗话说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:51.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know the old saying
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.69,0:11:54.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,彼之垃圾  我之财宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:54.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"One man's trash is another man's treasure"
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一次性的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Disposable?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.23,0:11:58.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,个屁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:11:58.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Phooey
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对于蟹老板  一切垃圾都是财宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For Mr. Krabs, all trash is treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:08.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,458)}清新剂
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.04,0:12:14.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生意开张了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:14.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open for business
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,淘到什么宝没
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See anything you like?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.85,0:12:19.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就花一块五买这把雨伞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:19.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll give you $1.50 for this umbrella
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.38,0:12:21.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才一块五
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:21.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,$1.50 for that?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可这是古董
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's an antique
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.73,0:12:24.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,曾经属于一个女王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:24.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It belonged to a queen
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.55,0:12:25.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要十块
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:25.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ten bucks
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十块
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ten bucks?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可上面全是孔洞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's full of holes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.53,0:12:30.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那女王是瑞士的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.53,0:12:30.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was the queen of Switzerland
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:30.89,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 瑞士奶酪多孔 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说女王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A queen, you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.73,0:12:33.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:33.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.81,0:12:36.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  瑞士没女王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:36.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, they don't have a queen
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.77,0:12:38.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那行  砍价老手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:38.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mr. Bargain Hunter
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.73,0:12:39.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:39.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Five bucks
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.23,0:12:40.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成交
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:40.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Deal
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.20,0:12:47.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全天候傻蛋的甜美香气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:47.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sweet smell of an all-day sucker
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:47.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(510,920)}超 大 棒 棒 糖
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.99,0:12:50.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃起来味道还更好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:50.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They taste even better
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.79,0:12:51.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:51.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.62,0:12:52.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:52.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在卖古董
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm having an antique sale
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.92,0:12:57.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到处来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:57.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have a look around
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.59,0:13:00.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  快看这玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:00.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, look at this thing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.30,0:13:01.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是好酷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:01.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty cool, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.60,0:13:04.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着好像我昨天扔掉的马桶塞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:03.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That looks like the toilet plunger
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I threw out yesterday
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不是马桶塞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That ain't no toilet plunger
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是个古董
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This here's an antique
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.85,0:13:09.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:09.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.60,0:13:14.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,17世纪的汤勺  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:14.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a 17th-century soup ladle, see?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我原来用法不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man, was I using mine wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.77,0:13:17.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:17.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.60,0:13:18.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五块
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:18.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Five bucks
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只有七块
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've only got seven
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.88,0:13:22.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成交
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:22.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Deal
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.78,0:13:26.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你这买家可真聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:26.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick Star, you are one smart shopper
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这酷毙了的汽水帽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at this neat-o soda-drinking hat
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.12,0:13:38.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它曾经肯定属于一个第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:38.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It must've belonged to someone who was number one
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.63,0:13:42.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有史以来  第一名都是屈指可数的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's only been a handful of number ones
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the entire history of forever
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.63,0:13:46.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而你就是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:46.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you're one of 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个帽子上写
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This hat says
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.86,0:13:50.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:50.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Hey, I'm number one
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.61,0:13:52.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我让重力来帮我喝饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:52.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I let gravity do my drinking"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这顶帽子就是为你打造的  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This hat was made for you, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你天生就是戴这顶帽子的料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were born to wear this hat
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很合身  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A perfect fit, eh, son?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.82,0:14:04.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你把我们带到了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:04.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you for bringing us together
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要怎么报答你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can I ever repay you?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.50,0:14:08.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,付十块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:08.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With ten dollars
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只有五块
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I have is five
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.25,0:14:13.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那怕是不能成交了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:13.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's no deal
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.33,0:14:15.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:15.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.75,0:14:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我找到了六毛八
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I found 68 cents
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.30,0:14:29.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过也许剩下的四块三毛二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:29.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But maybe you could take the other $4.32
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.00,0:14:30.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以从我工资扣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:30.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,out of my paycheck
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.32,0:14:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.60,0:14:33.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:33.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.68,0:14:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是看在你戴着帽子还挺帅的份上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But only 'cause you look so dashing in that hat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.29,0:14:42.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用谢  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:42.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.98,0:14:46.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是俩土包子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:46.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a couple of rubes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.09,0:14:47.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:47.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问你是不是这家珍品摊的承办商
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but are you the purveyor of this curio stand?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.61,0:14:50.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  正是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:50.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听说你在卖这顶稀有的新奇汽水帽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I understand you're selling
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:53.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this rare novelty drink hat
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(514,846)}汽水帽
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚卖掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fresh out
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听我解释
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me explain
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.34,0:15:00.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来要用五百块找你买那顶汽水帽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:15:00.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared to give you $500 for that drink hat
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五五五五五
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fi-fi-fi-fi-fi
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.04,0:15:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not so fast
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.75,0:15:06.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要出一千块换帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:06.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give you $1,000 for such a hat
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.59,0:15:13.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我出十万现金换你说的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:13.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give you $100,000 in cash for said hat
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.52,0:15:21.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生  我要用一百万买下那顶帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:21.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sir, I'll give you a million dollars for that hat
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.06,0:15:25.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:25.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在那  戴着我那值一百万的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There he is with me million-dollar hat
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须趁早拿回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to get it back
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然他就会发现帽子有多值钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before he finds out how much it's worth
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.62,0:15:37.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡的吹出量翻两倍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:37.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My bubble production has increased twofold
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.37,0:15:39.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多亏了你  帽帽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:39.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, Hatty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.75,0:15:40.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:40.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.87,0:15:41.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:41.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. K
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你古董卖的怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's the antique biz treating you?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.63,0:15:44.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个不用管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:44.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind that
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.46,0:15:45.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:45.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想在派大星面前说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to say this in front of Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这帽子让你看起来像个女的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That hat makes you look like a girl
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是漂亮妹子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I a pretty girl?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.59,0:15:53.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:53.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, um
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.56,0:15:54.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:54.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.16,0:15:54.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你美若天仙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:54.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  把帽子还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, now give me the hat back
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.95,0:16:01.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板  你亲口说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:01.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Krabs, you said it yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.94,0:16:03.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我天生就是戴这顶帽子的料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:03.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was born to wear this hat
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.91,0:16:05.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:05.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to give it back
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.41,0:16:07.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这顶帽子不能离我而去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:07.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't part with this hat now
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.73,0:16:09.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟我们一同经历了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:09.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not after all we've been through
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.91,0:16:11.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:11.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要叫你帽帽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll call you Hatty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.25,0:16:14.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这时候你就出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:14.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's when you showed up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且你也没有美若天仙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you're not beautiful either
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:31.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1278,1016)}帽子
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.04,0:16:29.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我正要找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:29.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, just the man I wanted to see
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.43,0:16:31.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是还在玩那顶破烂旧帽子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:31.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still playing with that dumb old hat, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.34,0:16:31.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:31.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.76,0:16:33.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那顶无聊的旧帽子还没玩腻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:33.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not sick of that boring old hat yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.34,0:16:37.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对那垃圾一点都不厌烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:37.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not tired of that old piece of junk?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.31,0:16:40.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一丁点都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:40.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not even a teensy, tiny bit?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.10,0:16:40.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:40.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.64,0:16:43.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你就应该不想看我袋子里的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:43.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then I guess you don't want to see what's in my bag
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1180,676)}帽子
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.98,0:16:44.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:44.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新奇古怪帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Novelty hats
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.29,0:16:47.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个带空调的怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:47.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about this air-conditioned one?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.98,0:16:51.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有点危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:51.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seems a little dangerous
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.41,0:16:52.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带榨汁机的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:52.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Juicer?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.74,0:16:55.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狐媚老大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:55.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Foxy Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:56.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1010,382)}狐媚老大爷
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你觉得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, what do you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.55,0:17:02.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用你的笨帽子换这些帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:02.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your silly hat for all these hats
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不成交  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No deal, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要跟帽帽一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sticking with Hatty
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.17,0:17:06.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过还是谢谢你的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:06.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the offer, though
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.75,0:17:09.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还以为狐媚老大爷肯定可以引他上钩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:09.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought the Foxy Grandpa would get him for sure
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来不想这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to have to do this
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但已经没有其他选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but he leaves me no other option
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须要使出惊吓手段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have to scare it off of him
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.73,0:17:27.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就能吓到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:27.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This'll scare him
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的老天爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:40.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(896,418)}奶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:40.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(896,590)}蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:40.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(896,760)}酪
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.41,0:17:38.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有浮空的购物单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:38.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A floating shopping list
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是购物单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not a shopping list
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a ghost
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.38,0:17:52.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:52.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, listen, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.67,0:17:57.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是汽水帽之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:57.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am the Ghost of Soda Drink Hats
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.51,0:17:58.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来这告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:58.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm here to tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.89,0:18:02.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你拥有的那顶汽水帽被诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:02.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that that soda drink hat you possess is cursed
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.68,0:18:03.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:03.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cursed?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.56,0:18:04.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:04.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.75,0:18:07.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它的原主现在已经故去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:07.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It once belonged to some guy who's dead now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.89,0:18:08.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原主是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:08.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What guy?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.77,0:18:11.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,史密提某某
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:11.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smitty something
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.48,0:18:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,史密提什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smitty what?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.03,0:18:13.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,史密提
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:13.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smitty
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.94,0:18:14.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,沃本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:14.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Werben
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.74,0:18:15.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,耶格曼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:15.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jaegerman
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.57,0:18:16.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,詹森
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:16.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jensen
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他以前肯定是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He must have been number one
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼怪世界的第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Number one in Bogeyland
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.82,0:18:21.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:21.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, listen
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.45,0:18:23.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上会有诅咒降临到你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:23.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a curse will descend on you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.41,0:18:26.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但只要马上把帽子还回去就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:26.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,unless the hat is returned to its owner immediately
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.93,0:18:27.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:27.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Immediately?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.91,0:18:29.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:29.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Immediately
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.67,0:18:30.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还给主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:30.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To its owner?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.79,0:18:31.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:31.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.88,0:18:32.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:32.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.96,0:18:33.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:33.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.75,0:18:37.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须马上还给它的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:37.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It must be returned to its owner right now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.01,0:18:37.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:37.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.88,0:18:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.80,0:18:40.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:40.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚去让那顶被诅咒的汽水帽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was returning the cursed soda drink hat
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.43,0:18:44.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,物归原主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:44.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to its original owner
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,史密提沃本耶格曼詹森
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smitty Werben Jaegerman Jensen
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.14,0:18:46.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:46.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.18,0:18:50.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就没有史密提沃本耶格曼詹森
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:50.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There is no Smitty Werben Jaegerman Jensen
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.32,0:18:51.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的有他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:51.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure there is
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.10,0:18:53.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就埋在浮尸公墓里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:53.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's buried out in Floater's Cemetery
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.07,0:18:53.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:53.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.84,0:18:54.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:54.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.43,0:18:54.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:54.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.96,0:18:55.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:55.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.49,0:18:57.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲子给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:57.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that shovel
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.65,0:19:00.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是他的帽子  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:00.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was his hat Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.86,0:19:03.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:03.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was number one
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.84,0:19:22.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷静下来  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:22.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold yourself together, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只是个墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just a boneyard
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到处是尸骨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,filled with bones
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.35,0:19:29.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:29.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.44,0:19:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's he doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.82,0:19:42.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里埋葬着章鱼哥的希望与梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:42.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Here lie Squidward's hopes and dreams"
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a baby
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.20,0:19:44.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我到哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:44.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where was I?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.99,0:19:45.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:45.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.83,0:19:47.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要找史密提那什么詹森
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:47.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotta find Smitty Whatsajipster
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:48.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(394,846)}老咸长眠于此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:48.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(986,380)}逝者安息
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.01,0:19:48.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:48.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:49.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(346,198)}逝者安息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:49.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(982,868)}潜水丹
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.87,0:19:49.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:49.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nope
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:50.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(900,820)}傻子
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.70,0:19:50.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:50.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1020,860)}我旁边的是傻子
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.66,0:19:51.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.50,0:19:51.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:51.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.42,0:19:52.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:52.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.04,0:19:53.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:53.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.94,0:19:54.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:54.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nope, not there
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.42,0:19:57.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整块墓园里的坟全都找遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:57.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've checked every headstone in this cemetery
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.81,0:20:00.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就没埋什么史密提沃吧啦吧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:20:00.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and there's no Smitty Wabbablabba buried here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.13,0:20:02.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快想想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:02.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.10,0:20:04.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许海绵宝宝的话里有什么线索
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:03.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe something SpongeBob said
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:04.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will give you some kind of clue
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了  舔门把手在外星球犯法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember, licking doorknobs
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is illegal on other planets
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.49,0:20:09.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是这句
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:09.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, not that
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.70,0:20:10.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你绝对猜不中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:10.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never guess
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.48,0:20:12.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我昨晚在我袜子里发现了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:12.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what I found in my sock last night
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.14,0:20:13.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去猜猜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:13.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, guess
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.63,0:20:15.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:15.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.03,0:20:17.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是他的帽子  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:17.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was his hat, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was number one
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我肯定找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never find
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:24.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(740,450)}史密提沃本
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:25.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(740,450)}曼詹森
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.74,0:20:26.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他家的坟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:26.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The grave
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.41,0:20:31.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会真的要为了钱刨他坟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:31.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I really going to defile this grave for money?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.91,0:20:33.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然要了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:33.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course I am
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,中奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jackpot
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.51,0:20:44.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快到爸爸这来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:44.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come to Papa
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,斯密提  放下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Smitty, let go
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.51,0:20:50.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碎碎平安  斯密提
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:50.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rest in pieces, Smitty
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.89,0:20:53.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,值一百万的帽子归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:53.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got the million-dollar hat
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.44,0:20:57.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老兄  那是我的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:57.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, man, that's my hat
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.99,0:20:58.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:20:58.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.98,0:20:59.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:20:59.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.73,0:21:00.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:00.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.48,0:21:03.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爬回你的坑里去  烂骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:03.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just crawl back into your hole, bone boy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.71,0:21:04.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点装死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:04.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, play dead
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.95,0:21:07.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来只能从你身上硬抢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:07.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm going to have to take it from you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.78,0:21:09.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对对对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:09.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.25,0:21:10.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就你一个能拿我怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:10.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You and what army?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.45,0:21:14.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有一大伙活死鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:14.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only the army of the living dead
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.01,0:21:16.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在深夜档的节目里看过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:16.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've seen this on the late show
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.83,0:21:18.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这些恶鬼要压制住我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:18.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ghoulish fiends hold me down
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.25,0:21:20.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轮流咬我的内脏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:20.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and take turns nibbling on my innards
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.09,0:21:23.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后吃掉我脑子  躯干都留给秃鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:23.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then you eat my brain and leave my body for the buzzards
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's disgusting
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.69,0:21:26.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱只是想把帽子拿回来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:26.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We just want the hat back
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想都别想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No flipping way
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,后退
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back up
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.07,0:21:31.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说后退
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:31.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back up, I say
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.26,0:21:32.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:32.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attack
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发现目标
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tallyho
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看我  我演侠盗罗宾汉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at me, I'm Errol Fin
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.32,0:21:39.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要散架了  骨头脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:39.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're falling apart, marrow brain
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.74,0:21:40.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:40.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must be kidding
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去洗洗睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back to oblivion
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们姐妹怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's your sister?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.41,0:21:47.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,骨头脑袋  游戏时间结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:47.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, boneheads, playtime's over
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.67,0:21:58.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一百万
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:21:58.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A million dollars
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.39,0:22:00.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一百万到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.39,0:22:00.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a million dollars
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.92,0:22:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.80,0:22:07.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:07.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.15,0:22:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种稀有的新奇古怪汽水帽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The rare novelty soda drink hat
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.05,0:22:12.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一百万起拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:12.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's start the bidding at $1 million
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.27,0:22:17.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是狮子大开口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:17.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you want that all at once?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.94,0:22:18.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一百万
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:18.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A million dollars
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.85,0:22:20.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怕是逗死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:20.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got to be kidding
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.07,0:22:23.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可怜的笨蛋没在逗你们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:23.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The poor sap's not kidding
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.48,0:22:24.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没听说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:24.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.61,0:22:26.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人发现了满满一仓库的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.61,0:22:26.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They found a whole warehouse full of them
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.90,0:22:28.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都不值钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:28.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're worthless
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:30.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(308,864)}垃圾
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.45,0:22:33.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来给蟹老板掌声鼓励吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:33.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's give Mr. Krabs a big hand
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.20,0:22:37.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在那个才值一百万
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:37.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, that's worth a million dollars
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.37,0:22:40.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孩子  别走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:40.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid, wait up
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.63,0:22:41.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我先看到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:41.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saw him first
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.54,0:22:44.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要给你十亿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:44.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give you $1 billion
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.55,0:22:47.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太让我心伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:47.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a spirit breaker
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.43,0:22:52.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:52.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a baby
